[So it is not only elderly Caucasian tourists who are susceptible to GI
illness on board cruise liners.
Komsomolsk is on the Amur river, about halfway between Khabarovsk, on the
Chinese border, and the river's mouth north of Sakhalin Island in the Sea
of Okhotsk, north of Japan - Mod.JW
